item.title: JDK help
item.dc:creator: @Siccc Siccc
item.description:
@Siccc wrote:

I hope you aren’t talking about me. I probally shouldn’t of called you retarded. Lmfao. Well anyways if you have the newest jdk this is what your compiler should look like.

@echo off Title building "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_16\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause

You may also have a folder in program files called sun.

So if you do put this in your compiler.

@echo off Title building "C:\Program Files\sun\sdk\jdk\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause
